'''Kost & Ko Factories''' was a manufacturer of the [[Deep Space Manufacturing Facility]], also known as the X7 Factory Station.

{{Company-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
This company is referenced in the tech-room stats for both [[Star Wars: TIE Fighter (video game)|''TIE Fighter'']] and [[Star Wars: X-Wing vs. TIE Fighter|''X-wing vs. TIE Fighter'']], but [[Star Wars: X-Wing Alliance|''X-wing Alliance'']] listed the manufacturer as the [[Telgorn Corporation/Legends|Telgorn Corporation]].

